
AeroSpeak Terminal is a Python-based application that translates text inputs into the NATO Phonetic Alphabet and provides real-time audio playback. Designed for enthusiasts and aviation communication practice.

## Features
- **Real-time Conversion:** Instantly translates your input into standard aviation phonetic codes.
- **Audio Synthesis:** Uses Google Text-to-Speech (gTTS) to read the codes aloud.
- **Reference Table:** Always-visible phonetic reference chart for quick access.

